fields.name: NordicTrack X22i Incline Trainer Treadmill
fields.description: Work out all over the world with an interactive personal trainer and discover an innovative fitness experience with a vibrant 22” Smart HD touchscreen and dynamic 40 percent incline.

fields.name: Reebok Jet 300 Series
fields.description: Featuring a powerful 2.5 HP motor, the Jet 300 is built for total home performance. Reaching 20 kph across 15 incline levels, the 300 offers all the tools to push your limits on every run. Fitted with a 7 window LED display and hand pulse sensors, the Bluetooth enabled console shows detailed performance feedback with built-in speakers to power your run. Run on air - designed with signature Air Motion technology, the Jet 300 reacts to each foot strike; transferring air between the cushioning pods to offer support where it’s needed. Compatible with the Reebok Fitness App, you’re able to tailor and track your workouts via your phone whilst running any route virtually through Google Street View.

fields.name: Reebok One GX40S Black Crosstrainer
fields.description: The Reebok GX40s ONE Series Cross Trainer provides a total body workout without the harsh impact on your joints. The higher the resistance (choose from 32 levels), the more exertion required to push down on the slip resistant foot plates and move the handlebars. If you’re looking to focus on the lower body only, grip the fixed handlebars as an alternative targeted exercise.20 console programs on the GX40s include 12 pre-set, 3 target (time, distance covered and calories burned), manual, watts control, heart rate control, recovery and 1 user defined program - so there’s plenty of options to choose from to make your workout unique every time.During your training program you can command the workout data you need to improve results; these can be easily monitored on the 5.5” LCD display. Plus, the cross trainer’s handlebars feature hand pulse sensors enabling you to pick up your heart rate at any time during the workout.Throughout the workout you’ll find the GX40s operates with minimal noise and is sturdy in its stature with floor level adjustment. If you need to move your cross trainer to another room in the house, no problem - the GX40s features integrated wheels for easy manoeuvrability. Assembling your cross trainer is fuss-free too. It comes with an assembly manual and clear labelling to ensure you’re guided through each step.

fields.name: Olympic Tri Grip Barbell set 100kg
fields.description: A hard-wearing set of weights is the backbone to any gym. The easy tri-grip plates boast a healthy blend of light and heavy weights. Slap the heavy plates on for your big lifts like squats and bench press, the light plates are ideal for slowly increasing your strength from there. Brass-bushings in the barbell smoothly rotate the ends for a balanced feel during lifts. Multiple knurling points along the bar support your grip, the high-performance nature of the barbell gives it such generous weight capacities. This is a weight set designed to grow with you.
